This product includes software and methods developed at Emory University
Library & Information Technology Services for the OHDSI "Mind Meets Machine"
(MMM) Vocabulary Edition challenge (OHDSI Europe Symposium, Rotterdam,
2026-04-19), where the Emory submission placed 1st overall.

